('Anyword', 'anyword', 'AI copywriting with predictive performance scoring', 'Anyword combines AI text generation with a unique predictive performance score that estimates how well your copy will convert. It analyzes your brand voice and audience data to produce on-brand marketing content across ads, emails, landing pages, and social posts.', 'https://anyword.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Starter","price":"$49/mo","features":["Unlimited words","Performance prediction","Blog wizard"]},{"plan":"Data-Driven","price":"$99/mo","features":["Copy intelligence","Brand voice","Target audience"]},{"plan":"Business","price":"$499/mo","features":["Custom AI models","Team workflows","Analytics"]}]', 'beginner', true, '{web,api}', '{"Predictive performance score","Brand voice training","Blog post wizard","Ad copy generator","Email copy","Landing page copy","A/B testing suggestions","Custom AI models"}', '{"HubSpot","Jasper","WordPress","Google Ads"}', 'https://anyword.com/api', true, '{"Marketing teams","Performance marketers","Copywriters"}', '{"Academic writing","Technical documentation"}', 'Strong differentiator with its performance prediction scoring, which sets it apart from generic AI writers. Best suited for data-driven marketing teams who want copy that converts.', now()),

('Writer', 'writer-ai', 'Enterprise AI writing platform for brand consistency', 'Writer is an enterprise-grade generative AI platform built for businesses that need on-brand, compliant content at scale. It enforces style guides, terminology, and tone across teams while offering AI text generation, rewriting, and content governance tools.', 'https://writer.com', 'paid', '[{"plan":"Team","price":"$18/user/mo","features":["Style guide","AI assistant","Snippets"]},{"plan":"Enterprise","price":"Custom","features":["Custom AI models","Knowledge graph","API access","SSO"]}]', 'intermediate', true, '{web,api,plugin}', '{"Brand voice enforcement","Style guide AI","Terminology management","AI text generation","Content governance","Knowledge graph","Custom AI models","Compliance checks"}', '{"Google Docs","Chrome","Figma","Contentful","HubSpot"}', 'https://developer.writer.com', true, '{"Enterprise content teams","Regulated industries","Brand managers"}', '{"Solo creators","Budget-conscious freelancers"}', 'The gold standard for enterprise AI writing. Excels at brand consistency and governance, though its price point puts it out of reach for smaller teams.', now()),

('Hypotenuse AI', 'hypotenuse-ai', 'AI content generation for e-commerce and product descriptions', 'Hypotenuse AI specializes in generating product descriptions, blog articles, and marketing copy tailored for e-commerce brands. It pulls from product data to create SEO-optimized content that matches your brand tone, with bulk generation for large catalogs.', 'https://hypotenuse.ai', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Starter","price":"$29/mo","features":["50,000 words","25 images","Blog writer"]},{"plan":"Growth","price":"$59/mo","features":["Unlimited words","Bulk generation","Brand voice"]},{"plan":"Enterprise","price":"Custom","features":["API access","Custom models","Dedicated support"]}]', 'beginner', true, '{web,api}', '{"Product description generator","Bulk content generation","SEO optimization","Brand voice matching","Image generation","Blog article writer","Social media copy","Catalog integration"}', '{"Shopify","WooCommerce","BigCommerce","WordPress"}', 'https://docs.hypotenuse.ai', true, '{"E-commerce brands","Product marketers","Catalog managers"}', '{"Long-form editorial","Technical writing"}', 'Purpose-built for e-commerce content at scale. The bulk generation and direct Shopify integration make it a time-saver for brands with large product catalogs.', now()),

('Simplified', 'simplified', 'All-in-one AI content creation and design platform', 'Simplified combines AI writing, graphic design, video editing, and social media scheduling in one platform. Teams can create blog posts, social graphics, short videos, and schedule everything from a single dashboard with AI assistance throughout.', 'https://simplified.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Free","price":"$0","features":["2,000 AI words","5 design projects"]},{"plan":"Small Team","price":"$30/mo","features":["50,000 AI words","Unlimited design","Brand kit"]},{"plan":"Business","price":"$50/mo","features":["Unlimited words","AI presenter","Priority support"]}]', 'beginner', false, '{web}', '{"AI writer","Graphic design editor","Video editor","Social media scheduler","Brand kit","AI image generation","Template library","Team collaboration"}', '{"Instagram","Facebook","Twitter","YouTube","TikTok","LinkedIn"}', 'https://help.simplified.com', true, '{"Small businesses","Social media managers","Content creators"}', '{"Enterprise teams needing deep analytics","Developers needing API access"}', 'A jack-of-all-trades that bundles writing, design, and scheduling into one affordable tool. Individual features are not best-in-class, but the convenience factor is hard to beat for small teams.', now()),

('Peppertype', 'peppertype', 'AI content marketing and generation platform', 'Peppertype.ai by Pepper Content helps marketing teams generate blog posts, social media captions, ad copy, and email content using AI. It includes a content quality audit feature and SEO suggestions to ensure high-performing output.', 'https://peppertype.ai', 'paid', '[{"plan":"Starter","price":"$35/mo","features":["50,000 words","35+ templates","Plagiarism check"]},{"plan":"Growth","price":"$199/mo","features":["Unlimited words","Content audit","Team workspace","SEO mode"]}]', 'beginner', true, '{web,api}', '{"AI content generation","Content audit scoring","SEO suggestions","35+ content templates","Plagiarism checker","Team workspace","Brand tone settings","Blog to social repurposing"}', '{"WordPress","Shopify","HubSpot","Semrush"}', 'https://docs.peppertype.ai', true, '{"Content marketing teams","Agencies","Blog-heavy brands"}', '{"Fiction writers","Non-English primary content"}', 'Solid AI content platform backed by Pepper Content marketplace. The content audit feature adds useful quality control that most AI writers lack.', now()),

('Scalenut', 'scalenut', 'AI-powered SEO content lifecycle management', 'Scalenut manages the entire content lifecycle from keyword research and topic clustering to AI-powered writing and real-time SEO optimization. It provides SERP-based outlines and NLP-driven content scoring to help pages rank.', 'https://scalenut.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Essential","price":"$39/mo","features":["100,000 AI words","5 SEO reports"]},{"plan":"Growth","price":"$79/mo","features":["Unlimited AI words","30 SEO reports","Cruise mode"]},{"plan":"Pro","price":"$149/mo","features":["75 SEO reports","Topic clusters","API"]}]', 'intermediate', true, '{web,api,plugin}', '{"Cruise mode long-form writer","SERP analysis","NLP content scoring","Topic clustering","Keyword planner","Real-time SEO optimization","Content brief generator","Chrome extension"}', '{"WordPress","Semrush","Google Search Console","Copyscape"}', 'https://scalenut.com/api-docs', true, '{"SEO content writers","Content agencies","SaaS marketers"}', '{"Non-SEO creative writing","Social media copy"}', 'One of the most complete SEO content platforms available. Cruise Mode can produce a full SEO-optimized article in minutes, though it still needs human editing for nuance.', now()),

('Frase', 'frase', 'AI-powered SEO content research and optimization', 'Frase helps content teams research, write, and optimize SEO content faster. It analyzes top SERP results to generate comprehensive briefs, provides an AI writer for drafting, and scores content in real time against ranking competitors.', 'https://frase.io', 'paid', '[{"plan":"Solo","price":"$15/mo","features":["4 articles/mo","AI writer","SERP analysis"]},{"plan":"Basic","price":"$45/mo","features":["30 articles/mo","AI writer"]},{"plan":"Team","price":"$115/mo","features":["Unlimited articles","Team collaboration","API"]}]', 'intermediate', true, '{web,api}', '{"SERP research","AI content briefs","Real-time content scoring","AI article writer","Question research","Competitor analysis","Outline builder","Content analytics"}', '{"Google Search Console","WordPress","Google Docs"}', 'https://frase.io/api', true, '{"SEO specialists","Content strategists","Freelance writers"}', '{"E-commerce product copy","Social media management"}', 'Excellent research-first approach to content creation. The SERP analysis and brief generation are among the best, making it ideal for writers who want data-driven outlines before they write.', now()),

('MarketMuse', 'marketmuse', 'AI content strategy and planning platform', 'MarketMuse uses AI to audit your existing content, identify gaps, and plan a content strategy that builds topical authority. It provides content briefs with target topics, word counts, and internal linking suggestions based on competitive analysis.', 'https://marketmuse.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Free","price":"$0","features":["10 queries/mo","Limited page analysis"]},{"plan":"Standard","price":"$149/mo","features":["100 queries/mo","Content briefs","Competitor analysis"]},{"plan":"Team","price":"$399/mo","features":["Unlimited queries","Team features","API"]}]', 'advanced', true, '{web,api}', '{"Content inventory audit","Topic modeling","Competitive content analysis","AI content briefs","Content scoring","Internal linking suggestions","Keyword difficulty","Personalized difficulty scores"}', '{"WordPress","Google Analytics","Google Search Console","Semrush"}', 'https://docs.marketmuse.com', true, '{"Content strategists","SEO directors","Enterprise publishers"}', '{"Casual bloggers","Small businesses with limited content"}', 'A strategic powerhouse for content planning and topical authority building. Expensive but delivers unique insights you cannot get from keyword tools alone.', now()),

('Clearscope', 'clearscope', 'Premium content optimization for search performance', 'Clearscope is a content optimization platform that uses NLP and competitor analysis to give writers real-time guidance on topics, terms, and readability needed to rank. Known for its simplicity and accuracy in content grading.', 'https://clearscope.io', 'paid', '[{"plan":"Essentials","price":"$170/mo","features":["10 content reports/mo","Google Docs integration"]},{"plan":"Business","price":"$1,200/mo","features":["100 reports/mo","API","Custom integrations"]},{"plan":"Enterprise","price":"Custom","features":["Unlimited reports","Dedicated support"]}]', 'intermediate', true, '{web,api}', '{"Content grading","NLP term suggestions","Readability scoring","Competitor content analysis","Google Docs integration","WordPress plugin","Keyword research","Content inventory"}', '{"Google Docs","WordPress","Semrush","Google Search Console"}', 'https://clearscope.io/api', true, '{"Enterprise SEO teams","Content agencies","B2B SaaS marketers"}', '{"Budget-conscious freelancers","Non-English content"}', 'The premium choice for content optimization with a clean, no-nonsense interface. Pricey, but its content grades correlate strongly with actual search rankings.', now()),

('INK Editor', 'ink-editor', 'AI writing and SEO assistant with real-time optimization', 'INK Editor combines AI writing with built-in SEO scoring, letting you draft and optimize content simultaneously. It offers a distraction-free editor, AI rewriting, and patent-pending SEO algorithms to maximize organic traffic potential.', 'https://inkforall.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Free","price":"$0","features":["Limited AI words","SEO scoring"]},{"plan":"Professional","price":"$39/mo","features":["Unlimited AI words","Full SEO tools","Keyword clustering"]},{"plan":"Enterprise","price":"$99/mo","features":["Team features","API","Priority support"]}]', 'beginner', true, '{web,desktop,api}', '{"AI writer","Real-time SEO scoring","Keyword clustering","Distraction-free editor","AI image generation","Content shield AI detection","Headline optimizer","Meta description generator"}', '{"WordPress","Google Docs","Shopify"}', 'https://inkforall.com/docs', true, '{"Bloggers","SEO content writers","Small business owners"}', '{"Enterprise content governance","Academic research"}', 'A solid mid-range option combining AI writing with SEO optimization in one editor. The AI content shield feature for reducing AI detection is a unique selling point.', now()),

('Longshot AI', 'longshot-ai', 'AI writer for long-form factual content with citations', 'Longshot AI specializes in creating long-form, factually accurate content with built-in fact-checking and source citations. It generates blog posts, articles, and reports while verifying claims against real-time web data to reduce hallucinations.', 'https://longshot.ai', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Free","price":"$0","features":["Limited generations","Basic templates"]},{"plan":"Pro","price":"$29/mo","features":["Unlimited generations","Fact-check","Custom templates"]},{"plan":"Team","price":"$59/mo","features":["Team workspace","API access","Integrations"]}]', 'beginner', true, '{web,api,plugin}', '{"Fact-checking engine","Source citations","Long-form blog writer","FactGPT real-time data","Custom templates","Workflow builder","Chrome extension","SEO integration"}', '{"WordPress","Google Docs","Semrush","Copyscape"}', 'https://longshot.ai/api-docs', true, '{"Content marketers","Journalists","Research writers"}', '{"Fiction writers","Social media micro-content"}', 'Stands out with its fact-checking and citation features, addressing the biggest concern with AI-generated content. A smart choice for writers producing factual, authoritative articles.', now()),

('Narrato', 'narrato', 'AI content workspace for teams and agencies', 'Narrato is an AI-powered content workspace that combines content planning, creation, collaboration, and publishing in one platform. It offers AI templates, SEO briefs, workflow automation, and a content marketplace for outsourcing.', 'https://narrato.io', 'paid', '[{"plan":"Pro","price":"$36/mo","features":["Unlimited projects","AI writer","SEO briefs"]},{"plan":"Business","price":"$76/mo","features":["Custom workflows","API access","Guest access","Analytics"]}]', 'beginner', false, '{web}', '{"AI content templates","Editorial calendar","SEO content briefs","Team workflow automation","Content marketplace","Publishing integrations","Project management","Style guides"}', '{"WordPress","Webflow","Google Docs","Slack","Zapier"}', 'https://narrato.io/help', true, '{"Content agencies","Marketing teams","Freelance content managers"}', '{"Solo bloggers","Technical documentation teams"}', 'A well-rounded content operations platform that fills the gap between AI writing tools and project management. The built-in marketplace for hiring writers is a nice bonus.', now()),

('ContentBot', 'contentbot', 'AI content generation and automation for marketers', 'ContentBot provides AI-powered content generation with automation flows that can create and publish content on autopilot. It offers blog post generation, paraphrasing, landing page copy, and a unique automation builder for hands-off content pipelines.', 'https://contentbot.ai', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Prepaid","price":"$0.5/1000 words","features":["Pay as you go","All templates"]},{"plan":"Starter","price":"$29/mo","features":["50,000 words","Automation flows"]},{"plan":"Premium","price":"$59/mo","features":["150,000 words","Advanced automation","API"]}]', 'beginner', true, '{web,api}', '{"AI blog writer","Content automation flows","Paraphrasing tool","Landing page generator","Press release writer","Auto-publish","Content imports","API access"}', '{"WordPress","Zapier","Medium","Shopify"}', 'https://contentbot.ai/api', true, '{"Digital marketers","Content agencies","Solopreneurs"}', '{"Enterprise teams","Highly regulated industries"}', 'The automation flow builder is the killer feature here, letting you set up recurring content pipelines. Good for marketers who want to put content generation on semi-autopilot.', now()),

('Writecream', 'writecream', 'AI copywriting with personalized outreach and icebreakers', 'Writecream generates marketing copy, blog posts, and personalized cold outreach messages using AI. Its standout feature is AI-generated icebreakers and personalized intros for cold emails and LinkedIn messages based on prospect data.', 'https://writecream.com', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Free","price":"$0","features":["Limited credits","Basic templates"]},{"plan":"Unlimited","price":"$29/mo","features":["Unlimited credits","All templates","Personalization"]},{"plan":"Extended","price":"$49/mo","features":["Priority support","Team features","API"]}]', 'beginner', true, '{web,api,plugin}', '{"Cold email icebreakers","LinkedIn personalization","Blog article writer","Ad copy generator","Voice over generation","Image generation","Podcast script writer","Chrome extension"}', '{"LinkedIn","Gmail","HubSpot","Outreach"}', 'https://writecream.com/api', true, '{"Sales teams","Outreach specialists","Growth hackers"}', '{"Long-form editorial content","Academic writing"}', 'Niche but effective for personalized cold outreach. The AI icebreaker feature saves hours of prospect research, though general writing capabilities are average compared to competitors.', now()),

('Koala Writer', 'koala-writer', 'AI SEO article writer with real-time SERP analysis', 'Koala Writer (KoalaWriter) generates SEO-optimized articles by analyzing top search results in real time. It produces well-structured long-form content with proper headings, internal links, and FAQ sections that are ready to publish with minimal editing.', 'https://koala.sh', 'freemium', '[{"plan":"Essentials","price":"$9/mo","features":["15,000 words","GPT-4o","SERP analysis"]},{"plan":"Professional","price":"$25/mo","features":["45,000 words","Real-time data","Amazon reviews"]},{"plan":"Premium","price":"$49/mo","features":["100,000 words","Bulk generation","API"]}]', 'beginner', true, '{web,api}', '{"One-click SEO articles","Real-time SERP analysis","Amazon product roundups","FAQ generation","Internal linking","Outline editor","Bulk article generation","WordPress integration"}', '{"WordPress","Shopify","Google Search Console"}', 'https://koala.sh/docs', true, '{"Affiliate marketers","Niche site builders","SEO content writers"}', '{"Brand storytelling","Technical documentation"}', 'One of the best tools for churning out SEO-focused articles quickly. The Amazon roundup feature is perfect for affiliate marketers, though output still benefits from human polish.', now())

